SDL2

Download SDL2
https://www.libsdl.org/download-2.0.php
Windows Development Library
https://www.libsdl.org/release/SDL2-devel-2.0.12-mingw.tar.gz

Extract SDL2
e.g.
C:\dev\

Add SDL2 to PATH
e.g.
C:\dev\SDL2-2.0.12\i686-w64-mingw32\bin

MINGW

Download MinGW (32bit)
https://osdn.net/projects/mingw/
mingw-get-setup.exe

Install MinGW
e.g.
C:\MinGW\

Configure Make (optional)
https://stackoverflow.com/a/32127632
copy mingw32-make.exe
rename copy to make.exe 

Add MinGW to PATH
e.g.
C:\MinGW\bin

Setup Visual Studio Code intellisense
https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/cpp/config-mingw
https://stackoverflow.com/a/57463607
install c/c++ extension
open [project path]\.vscode\c_cpp_properties.json
update configurations:
    "includePath": [
        "${workspaceFolder}/**",
        "C:\\dev\\SDL2-2.0.12\\i686-w64-mingw32\\include\\SDL2",
        "C:\\dev\\SDL2_image-2.0.5\\i686-w64-mingw32\\include\\SDL2",
        "C:\\Program Files (x86)\\cmocka\\include"
    ],

cmocka

download windows installer
https://cmocka.org/files/1.1/

Add cmocka to PATH
C:\Program Files (x86)\cmocka\bin
